subscription_alternative.monthly_limit: Usage limits apply; higher limits during peak times compared to GPT-4o Mini/GPT-3.5. Up to 5x more usage for GPT-4o than free users.
5x higher usage limits than the free tier, with access to the highest capacity model (Claude 3.5 Sonnet).

pricing_analysis.trend: Aggressive price competition and rapid cost reduction in 2024, driven by new model architectures (e.g., OpenAI's GPT-4o) and pressure from highly efficient open-source models (Llama, DeepSeek, Qwen). Output costs remain significantly higher than input costs across all providers.
